<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 00:31:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普的刑事审判，寻找公正陪审团的挑战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-criminal-trial-challenges-in-finding-impartial-jury/articleshow/109328143.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109328143.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;纽约特朗普审判的陪审团遴选过程因偏见问题而受到损害，阻碍了公正陪审团的组建。尽管努力解决贿赂和匿名等问题，但复杂的甄选过程预计将持续数周。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-criminal-trial-challenges-in-finding-impartial-jury/articleshow/109328143.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔的喜马拉雅山坡上生长着日本冰冷的现金</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/on-himalayan-hillsides-in-nepal-grows-japans-cold-hard-cash/articleshow/109328458.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109328458.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在尼泊尔东部，小熊猫在夏尔巴人为日本日元纸供应时玩耍。 Kanpou Inc. 帮助地震后的尼泊尔农民重新设计日元。尼泊尔在农村面临挑战的情况下出口三俣材料。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/on-himalayan-hillsides-in-nepal-grows-japans-cold-hard-cash/articleshow/109328458.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚警方称韦克利教堂持刀伤人事件为恐怖事件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/stabbing-at-wakeley-church-a-terror-incident-australian-police-say/articleshow/109328032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109328032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/stabbing-at-wakeley-church-a-terror-incident-australian-police-say/articleshow/109328032.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列盟友敦促克制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-allies-urge-restraint/articleshow/109328486.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109328486.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗袭击后，以色列面临避免冲突的压力。内塔尼亚胡召集战时内阁，承诺做出回应。拜登警告以色列不要采取行动。加沙战争引发冲突。欧洲领导人敦促克制，对制裁进行了辩论。俄罗斯对伊朗的袭击持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-allies-urge-restraint/articleshow/109328486.cms</guid></item><item><title>喜鹊与好友宠物狗分居后重聚引发众怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/magpie-reunited-with-bff-pet-dog-after-separation-sparks-outrage/articleshow/109328371.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109328371.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在公众的愤怒之后，喜鹊莫莉与一只宠物狗团聚。黄金海岸夫妇朱丽叶·威尔斯 (Juliette Wells) 和里斯·莫滕森 (Reece Mortensen) 在接受野生动物护理人员培训后获得了执照。奥拉夫·肖尔茨（Olaf Scholz）就在德国吸食大麻一事向中国学生保证。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/magpie-reunited-with-bff-pet-dog-after-separation-sparks-outrage/articleshow/109328371.cms</guid></item><item><title>悉尼连续发生刺伤事件：一名主教和另外三人在教堂内遭到袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/back-to-back-stabbings-in-sydney-a-bishop-3-others-attacked-in-church/articleshow/109328504.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109328504.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;悉尼持刀袭击主教 Mar Mari Emmanuel 受伤。冲突后韦克利被捕。现场直播教堂活动。毕肖普的在线布道很受欢迎。被捕男子的动机仍未公开。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 00:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/back-to-back-stabbings-in-sydney-a-bishop-3-others-attacked-in-church/articleshow/109328504.cms</guid></item><item><title>先进的“DragonFire”激光器可能会改变乌克兰对俄罗斯的战争战略</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/advanced-dragonfire-laser-could-transform-ukraines-war-strategy-against-russia/articleshow/109321216.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109321216.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于乌克兰仍然顽固地防御俄罗斯的长期入侵，它正处于可能获得英国先进的“龙火”高功率激光武器原型的边缘。经过七年多的开发，该武器在最近的测试中展示了其精度，标志着两国军事技术的重大进步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/advanced-dragonfire-laser-could-transform-ukraines-war-strategy-against-russia/articleshow/109321216.cms</guid></item><item><title>弗朗西斯·斯科特基大桥倒塌：联邦调查局对巴尔的摩桥梁倒塌事件展开刑事调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/francis-scott-key-bridge-collapse-fbi-opens-criminal-probe-into-baltimores-bridge-collapse/articleshow/109317046.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109317046.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联邦调查局目前正在调查巴尔的摩弗朗西斯·斯科特基桥的悲惨倒塌事件，重点关注导致事故发生的情况，并确定是否遵守所有联邦法律。​​​调查是在“大理”号货轮上进行的，是由一位不愿透露姓名的消息人士向美联社透露的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/francis-scott-key-bridge-collapse-fbi-opens-criminal-probe-into-baltimores-bridge-collapse/articleshow/109317046.cms</guid></item><item><title>“芝加哥活动人士因伊朗袭击以色列而爆发欢呼”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/activists-in-chicago-erupt-in-cheers-over-irans-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109321233.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109321233.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在芝加哥，一群自称为反战活动人士的人在听到伊朗导弹和无人机袭击以色列的消息后欢呼雀跃。这一事件发生在“March On DNC 2024”和“Anti War Chicago”团体的一次会议期间。据军方报告称，周六晚上，伊朗向以色列领土发射了 300 多枚导弹和无人机，这些导弹和无人机主要被以色列及其盟国拦截。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/activists-in-chicago-erupt-in-cheers-over-irans-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109321233.cms</guid></item><item><title>堪萨斯州妇女失踪案，四人被捕，俄克拉荷马州农村发现两具尸体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-bodies-found-in-rural-oklahoma-after-4-arrested-in-case-of-missing-kansas-women/articleshow/109320117.cms</link><description>与绑架和谋杀两名堪萨斯州妇女有关的四人被捕后，俄克拉荷马州农村地区发现了两具尸体。来自堪萨斯州雨果顿的 27 岁维罗妮卡·巴特勒 (Veronica Butler) 和 39 岁吉利安·凯利 (Jilian Kelley) 正准备去接巴特勒的孩子参加生日聚会，但从未抵达。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:54:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-bodies-found-in-rural-oklahoma-after-4-arrested-in-case-of-missing-kansas-women/articleshow/109320117.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊姆兰·汗指控妻子“中毒”后，布什拉·比比向高等法院寻求医疗检查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bushra-bibi-moves-high-court-seeks-medical-examination-after-imran-khan-alleges-wife-being-poisoned/articleshow/109317050.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109317050.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布什拉·比比 (Bushra Bibi) 涉嫌中毒后前往肖卡特·卡努姆 (Shaukat Khanum) 医院接受体检。伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 的 PTI 要求进行考试。没有发现中毒证据。 Bibi 出现胃痛、食欲异常和舌苔。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bushra-bibi-moves-high-court-seeks-medical-examination-after-imran-khan-alleges-wife-being-poisoned/articleshow/109317050.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦当局宣布西南部进入紧急状态，闪电和降雨造成 41 人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-lightning-rains-kill-people-in-pakistan-as-authorities-declare-a-state-of-emergency-in-southwest/articleshow/109316487.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109316487.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;官员周一表示，过去三天，巴基斯坦西南部当局宣布进入紧急状态，闪电和暴雨已造成巴基斯坦各地至少 36 人死亡，其中大部分是农民。阿尔凡·卡蒂亚说，大多数死亡事件是由于闪电击中旁遮普省东部收割小麦的农民以及降雨导致房屋倒塌而造成的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-lightning-rains-kill-people-in-pakistan-as-authorities-declare-a-state-of-emergency-in-southwest/articleshow/109316487.cms</guid></item><item><title>高科技防御：以色列如何“迷惑”伊朗无人机和导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/high-tech-defense-how-israel-managed-to-confuse-iranian-drones-and-missiles/articleshow/109311061.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109311061.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/high-tech-defense-how-israel-managed-to-confuse-iranian-drones-and-missiles/articleshow/109311061.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对以色列的袭击引发了避免全面战争的竞赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-attack-on-israel-sparks-race-to-avert-a-full-blown-war/articleshow/109310471.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109310471.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-attack-on-israel-sparks-race-to-avert-a-full-blown-war/articleshow/109310471.cms</guid></item><item><title>苹果否认在 Epic Games 诉讼中违反美国法院命令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/apple-denies-violating-us-court-order-in-epic-games-lawsuit/articleshow/109310260.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109310260.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;苹果驳斥了有关其 App Store 违抗法院命令的指控，并请求加州联邦法官驳回 Epic Games 藐视法庭的请求。这家科技巨头在向美国地区法官伊冯·冈萨雷斯·罗杰斯 (Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers) 提交的文件中捍卫了自己的立场，后者负责监督 Epic 2020 年指控苹果违反反垄断法的诉讼。在关于应用程序分发和应用内支付法规的持续法律斗争中，苹果公司的立场仍然坚定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/apple-denies-violating-us-court-order-in-epic-games-lawsuit/articleshow/109310260.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯表示对中东紧张局势升级极为担忧并敦促克制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-its-extremely-concerned-by-rise-in-middle-east-tensions-urges-restraint/articleshow/109309926.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109309926.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯对伊朗袭击以色列后中东紧张局势感到担忧，并敦促克制和政治解决。克里姆林宫发言人表示，重大分歧只能通过政治和外交手段解决。伊朗采取行动是对大使馆袭击的回应。俄罗斯避免批评伊朗。加沙战争导致紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-its-extremely-concerned-by-rise-in-middle-east-tensions-urges-restraint/articleshow/109309926.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国对维权人士家属进行“集体惩罚”：人权组织</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-using-collective-punishment-against-activists-families-rights-group/articleshow/109309585.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109309585.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据一个人权组织周一发出的警报，在对民间社会不断升级的打压中，中国人权活动人士的后代正面临着父母倡导的影响。中国经常被指责在新疆、西藏以及现在的香港压制人权。北京反驳了这些说法，将其归咎于对其进步的抹黑运动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-using-collective-punishment-against-activists-families-rights-group/articleshow/109309585.cms</guid></item><item><title>新加坡总理李显龙下台； 5月15日将权力移交给继任者黄</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-pm-lee-steps-down-to-hand-over-power-to-successor-wong-on-may-15/articleshow/109308126.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109308126.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:21:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-pm-lee-steps-down-to-hand-over-power-to-successor-wong-on-may-15/articleshow/109308126.cms</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨向中国学生保证，我们在德国并不都吸大麻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/we-dont-all-smoke-weed-in-germany-scholz-assures-chinese-students/articleshow/109308323.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109308323.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;肖尔茨是在回答同济大学一名学生的提问时发表上述言论的。该学生询问，如果他在德国学习，是否必须吸食大麻，因为这种药物在中国并不合法。德国二月份通过了大麻合法化立法，允许个人和协会种植和拥有有限数量的大麻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:25:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/we-dont-all-smoke-weed-in-germany-scholz-assures-chinese-students/articleshow/109308323.cms</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列战时内阁将于格林威治标准时间 1100 点重新召开会议，应对伊朗对峙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-war-cabinet-to-reconvene-at-1100-gmt-in-iran-standoff-source-says/articleshow/109307986.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109307986.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:15:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-war-cabinet-to-reconvene-at-1100-gmt-in-iran-standoff-source-says/articleshow/109307986.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>